 "transcript": [
  {
   "start": 0.16,
   "end": 6.94,
   "text": "Hey, what's up? Living in Boulder Vlog with Kyle Pounds, uh, for the 4th of January, 2013."
  },
  {
   "start": 7.1,
   "end": 12.88,
   "text": "It's 7.07 in the morning right now, as you can see from all the dag-dog snow all yonder."
  },
  {
   "start": 13.06,
   "end": 14.58,
   "text": "Um, I mean, the light coming out."
  },
  {
   "start": 15.46,
   "end": 21.62,
   "text": "I've been up all night, uh, because I'm kind of becoming nocturnal, but, um, yeah, but"
  },
  {
   "start": 21.62,
   "end": 22.18,
   "text": "Which I like."
  },
  {
   "start": 22.22,
   "end": 23.68,
   "text": "I like working on my schedule, dude."
  },
  {
   "start": 23.92,
   "end": 30.69,
   "text": "I really was getting off on it when I was in, um, Scandinavia, dude."
  },
  {
   "start": 30.69,
   "end": 32.49,
   "text": "Those guys really live on their own schedule."
  },
  {
   "start": 32.65,
   "end": 34.73,
   "text": "At least they had the opportunity to, I guess, if they were for themselves."
  },
  {
   "start": 34.85,
   "end": 42.06,
   "text": "Anyways, um, so my V-Log, I just peed and I was like, oh shit, did I do my V-Log yet?"
  },
  {
   "start": 42.16,
   "end": 43.06,
   "text": "And I didn't."
  },
  {
   "start": 44.4,
   "end": 47.98,
   "text": "Um, so, uh, yesterday, what did I do?"
  },
  {
   "start": 48.16,
   "end": 52.9,
   "text": "Um, well, I was up until, like, I can't remember how late I was up."
  },
  {
   "start": 53.22,
   "end": 54.72,
   "text": "It was, like, after sunrise."
  },
  {
   "start": 55.22,
   "end": 58.94,
   "text": "So then I crashed and I got up at, like, 3 in the afternoon or whatever."
  },
  {
   "start": 58.94,
   "end": 67.88,
   "text": "And, um, and, uh, I, I, I finished my weed yesterday, but I got to get, so I, I busted"
  },
  {
   "start": 67.88,
   "end": 70.02,
   "text": "Through $30 with the weed in two days, dude."
  },
  {
   "start": 70.18,
   "end": 74.22,
   "text": "That's, $15 a day on weed is not something that I can do."
  },
  {
   "start": 74.7,
   "end": 80.02,
   "text": "So I'm kind of glad that, um, but, you know, the prices are higher now than they're going"
  },
  {
   "start": 80.02,
   "end": 81.68,
   "text": "To be later on because there's just so much demand."
  },
  {
   "start": 81.74,
   "end": 86.74,
   "text": "Like I saw in the Young Turks at the beginning, it was $25 an eighth, which I find extremely"
  },
  {
   "start": 86.74,
   "end": 87.56,
   "text": "Hard to believe."
  },
  {
   "start": 87.68,
   "end": 89.26,
   "text": "I don't know where they got that fucking information from."
  },
  {
   "start": 89.8,
   "end": 91.92,
   "text": "And then by the end of the day, it was like $70, but I paid $60."
  },
  {
   "start": 92.2,
   "end": 97.38,
   "text": "But, um, but yesterday morning or afternoon, I got up and I, uh, I saw I had a little bit"
  },
  {
   "start": 97.38,
   "end": 102.12,
   "text": "Of weed lift in my, uh, pen and then I scraped the pipe and I got high."
  },
  {
   "start": 103.36,
   "end": 105.68,
   "text": "And, uh, anyways, so yesterday I was high."
  },
  {
   "start": 107.04,
   "end": 107.28,
   "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
   "start": 107.68,
   "end": 109.08,
   "text": "And then I worked all day long."
  },
  {
   "start": 109.22,
   "end": 111.68,
   "text": "I didn't ride the bike because I was high and I didn't want to try, you know, because"
  },
  {
   "start": 111.68,
   "end": 114.22,
   "text": "This, because I knew yesterday was the last day I was going to be high and I was going"
  },
  {
   "start": 114.22,
   "end": 120.38,
   "text": "To sober up, which led me in to go and get a couple of, um, these like 8%, um, drinks"
  },
  {
   "start": 120.38,
   "end": 124.36,
   "text": "Made by, uh, my, by, uh, Budweiser."
  },
  {
   "start": 124.78,
   "end": 127.54,
   "text": "They're these margarita drinks and I drank one and I got all buzzed."
  },
  {
   "start": 127.54,
   "end": 128.78,
   "text": "So I was like, fuck it, get another one."
  },
  {
   "start": 128.8,
   "end": 134.52,
   "text": "So I got another one and it didn't really, I don't recall it getting me buzzed anymore."
  },
  {
   "start": 134.74,
   "end": 136.46,
   "text": "I think I took too much time drinking it."
  },
  {
   "start": 137.36,
   "end": 140.74,
   "text": "If you want to get a buzz, dude, make sure you have to drink that shit fast."
  },
  {
   "start": 140.74,
   "end": 143.36,
   "text": "You can't nurse it over the course of a couple of hours."
  },
  {
   "start": 144.5,
   "end": 146.26,
   "text": "So anyways, I was working all day long."
  },
  {
   "start": 146.36,
   "end": 146.8,
   "text": "I've been listening."
  },
  {
   "start": 147.02,
   "end": 159.45,
   "text": "I listened to, I listened to the course, uh, or the, um, the, uh, um, the court of Scientology"
  },
  {
   "start": 159.45,
   "end": 161.63,
   "text": "Against Scientology hearings in 1982."
  },
  {
   "start": 162.49,
   "end": 163.73,
   "text": "And I finished that whole thing."
  },
  {
   "start": 163.79,
   "end": 165.67,
   "text": "Now I'm listening to interviews with L. Ron Hubbard."
  },
  {
   "start": 165.73,
   "end": 169.85,
   "text": "I'm like, I'm like riveted with this whole Scientology stuff."
  },
  {
   "start": 169.91,
   "end": 170.91,
   "text": "I'm going to do a video about it."
  },
  {
   "start": 170.91,
   "end": 174.77,
   "text": "Um, I thought probably might, that'll be my next video that I do like in depth about"
  },
  {
   "start": 174.77,
   "end": 177.49,
   "text": "Something, but I want to watch all this stuff."
  },
  {
   "start": 179.73,
   "end": 183.67,
   "text": "Um, so, um, yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 186.0,
   "end": 190.6,
   "text": "So, uh, I guess that's that with my V log living in Boulder V log."
  },
  {
   "start": 191.22,
   "end": 194.28,
   "text": "I saw, I ran actually two movies yesterday."
  },
  {
   "start": 194.66,
   "end": 199.64,
   "text": "Um, one of them was a cartoon turbo."
  },
  {
   "start": 199.84,
   "end": 200.62,
   "text": "That was pretty funny."
  },
  {
   "start": 200.7,
   "end": 201.28,
   "text": "That was pretty good."
  },
  {
   "start": 201.28,
   "end": 212.6,
   "text": "Um, I like cartoons, these new cartoons cause they're just so well filmed and, um, um, it's"
  },
  {
   "start": 212.6,
   "end": 213.52,
   "text": "Cool when you're stoned."
  },
  {
   "start": 213.96,
   "end": 215.56,
   "text": "They're cool to look at when you're fucking high."
  },
  {
   "start": 215.64,
   "end": 217.48,
   "text": "I can't wait until they come out with 3D TVs."
  },
  {
   "start": 218.4,
   "end": 219.8,
   "text": "Anyways, that's enough V logging."
  },
